Merck and Co Inc said a combinationheart drug is available by prescription in the U.S.    The drug is Vaseretic, a once-a-day medication combining anangiotensin converting enzyme inhibitor (ACE) and a diuretic totreat high blood pressure. The inhibitor is a new class ofantihypertensive drugs. Last year Merck introduced Vasotec, anACE inhibitor.    The new drug combined Vasotec and HydroDiuril, a frequentlyprescribed diuretic. Reuter&#3;